    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《诺托里阿之书》融合了经典的<strong>“建造、制作、生存”</strong>玩法，带你踏上一段未知而奇妙的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以独自冒险，也可以与好友一同探索充满谜团和挑战的神秘世界，建立据点、收集资源、发展势力，以及对抗形态各异的附魅者。途中，你可以专注单人探索，也可以招募冒险者组建小队，自由切换角色协同作战，逐步揭开附魅者的真相。重建希望，还是坠入毁灭？你的选择将改写王国的命运。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>广袤天地，生存有道</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在森林、田野、地下城等危机四伏的开放世界中自由探索，你将见证魔法造就的令人惊叹的风景。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潜入漆黑的深渊与冰封的洞窟、穿越古老的魔法遗迹与炽热的奴役者巢穴，与不同种类的附魅者战斗。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入激烈的BOSS战，对抗那些足以毁灭尘世的大型腐化生物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074620/extras/3c517e0a73cb9033320f9dd2ba12aee0.poster.avif?t=1764313224\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074620/extras/3c517e0a73cb9033320f9dd2ba12aee0.webm?t=1764313224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074620/extras/3c517e0a73cb9033320f9dd2ba12aee0.mp4?t=1764313224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  <strong>掌控魔法，构筑战队</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索六大魔法流派（火焰、冰霜、毒素、雷电、混沌、神圣），每种魔法拥有独特的战斗风格与效果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由搭配魔法符印与特技系统，调节参数，创造独一无二的法术组合。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为装备注入魔法、赋予元素属性，打造个性化的战斗体系。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >构建由数位冒险者组成的小队，在战斗中自由切换控制角色。每名队员都有其专属武器、技能与战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074620/extras/628938aadc682315603f637a5708114a.poster.avif?t=1764313224\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074620/extras/628938aadc682315603f637a5708114a.webm?t=1764313224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074620/extras/628938aadc682315603f637a5708114a.mp4?t=1764313224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>加入派系，拓展势力</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索不同派系，提升在派系中的地位，你将逐渐扩大在王国中的影响力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >指挥派系成员完成采集资源、守卫前哨阵地、锻造魔法武器、研究制作工艺等日常任务。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同派系的路线将引你进入截然不同的任务链与剧情分支，影响王国的命运与结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074620/extras/f2a2fc2e469bee228f4c91a65f9a08f5.poster.avif?t=1764313224\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074620/extras/f2a2fc2e469bee228f4c91a65f9a08f5.webm?t=1764313224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074620/extras/f2a2fc2e469bee228f4c91a65f9a08f5.mp4?t=1764313224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>丰富采集，建造家园</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >修建造型丰富的建筑，自定义其表面纹理和颜色，打造私人定制的生活空间、战斗防御系统和商业场所。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解放双手的自动化采集设施，专注建造乐趣，少做伐木工。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >资源储存至全局资源箱，无需占用背包空间，随时取用，建造效率飙升。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驯服野生动物，获取生活资源。下达命令，让猛兽来保护你的领地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074620/extras/c5892343affe8c2063e720b484a8e5e4.poster.avif?t=1764313224\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074620/extras/c5892343affe8c2063e720b484a8e5e4.webm?t=1764313224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074620/extras/c5892343affe8c2063e720b484a8e5e4.mp4?t=1764313224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>并肩作战，共同探险</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在线上多人PVE模式中，你可以与最多三位好友一起探索诺托里阿之书的世界。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >邀请你的朋友们一起体验剧情故事、攻克地下城、打造壮观的根据地，谱写属于你们的传奇故事吧！</p></li></ul>",
